      ],
      "description": "Writhing tentacles protrude from the face of the Nightbane! They can be situated anywhere in the face; some examples include the chin for a “living beard” look, between the nose and mouth for a Lovecraftian appearance, or instead of hair for a Medusa-like look. Bonuses: +2D6 to S.D.C. and +1D4 to Horror Factor.",
