          "gameSystem": "nightbane",
          "reference": "Nightbane Core Rulebook",
          "pageNumber": 103
        }
      ],
      "description": "The Nightbane has a perfectly smooth face: no eyes, mouth, or nose are visible. The creature can speak, but the voice seems to be coming from inside the smooth surface, and may have an inhuman quality, or simply sound muffled; player’s choice. The lack of eyes does not impair the Nightbane’s senses; he can see, smell and hear perfectly. To eat, food is seemingly pushed through the skin, like a soft membrane, where the mouth should be. Bonus: +1D4 to Horror Factor.",
