          "reference": "Nightbane Survival Guide (WB5)",
          "pageNumber": 99
        }
      ],
      "description": "This Nightbane’s ears are not those of a normal human, but any of the following: 01-20% large canine-like, 21-40% large and pointed, 41-60% pointed and has 1D6+4 peircings, 61-80% tiny, flat and noticeable only when one looks closely, 81-00% literally elephant ears or something large and alien looking (covered in spikes or spines, unusual shape, etc.). Regardless of their appearance, they provide exceptional hearing, roughly equal to that of a dog. Bonuses: +4 on Perception Rolls involving sound and +1 on initiative. Penalties: -1 from P.B., and Undercover Ops, and high-pitched sound hurts the ears (-2 on initiative and no Perception Roll bonus).",
